{"tid":1863373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"追上北上廣深確診數字是林鄭政治任務","createTime":"2020-02-05T06:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T09:06:12.000Z","uid":308853,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e89e7fbaeeeac2eed618ffb5de0ba344e5e0e7f8","tid":1863373,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:15:00.000Z","msg":"按今日（2月5日）衛生防護中心的公佈，北上廣深確診武漢肺炎人數，截至2月5日09:00:<br />\n<br />\n北京 228<br />\n上海 233<br />\n<br />\n至2月4日深夜12晚:<br />\n<br />\n廣州 237<br />\n深圳 289<br />\n<br />\n而香港是---18<br />\n<br />\n有理由相信亞爺曾經明示暗示，香港疫症不能太少，否則有以下憂慮:<br />\n<br />\n1 國內民眾會好奇是否香港制度較優越?真的內地比較落後? 連北上廣深都比香港落後? 或者中央對港有特殊優惠，提早通報疫情?<br />\n<br />\n2 西方國家會藉此評論香港的西方式自由社會比內地制度先進。連人命都可保障<br />\n<br />\n因此林鄭目前必需在明在暗令香港確診人數追上內地一線城市，否則亞爺冇面，人民燥動。"},{"pid":"ce2ffcffabfca58a64b7e338b724a1c253f77e82","tid":1863373,"uid":126889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"阿咩爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33999b0fafb25527cca3f6d07b862f8a0c4c79d0","tid":1863373,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"九個月來，<br />\n甴種同淋病做嘅嘢，<br />\n有邊樣唔係要殘害香港?"},{"pid":"4620f5f359424578561edfbcf13059bab232b765","tid":1863373,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"我有諗過係中央要懲罰香港，報復反送中運動，不過呢點同呢個post無關"},{"pid":"69a813f532930738e02debff40b9beb6604acdaf","tid":1863373,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:33:58.000Z","msg":"不成立，要化武攻擊直接叫速龍運動體病毒<br />\n<br />\n純粹仲係止暴制亂mode ，同唔可以帶頭封關，等國際慢慢封香港<br />\n<br />\n澳洲小粉紅已證白手套用途"},{"pid":"01d40464fdf92e1f806c6ad4cdba45aec26ca6b4","tid":1863373,"uid":42395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"爺乜尻"},{"pid":"a6f3ef2a2bc95259bd80947efda09469eff1f6b4","tid":1863373,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"封關靠自己啦<br />\n（不做病人第一收容港）封關行動，從對付跨境巴士開始，繼而其他中資<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863318</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d235a08506e364eb6ec764542804c63c4d4a1373","tid":1863373,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:57:36.000Z","msg":"未必關事, 喺武漢/湖北去北上廣深容易過黎香港"},{"pid":"e875ff99ac0212fe7a05efbfb4ab7fa8d6f91e34","tid":1863373,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3a0196a681c5058606429cb58fd83210dae516","tid":1863373,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d235a08506e364eb6ec764542804c63c4d4a1373","tid":1863373,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:57:36.000Z","msg":"未必關事, 喺武漢/湖北去北上廣深容易過黎香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:06:12.000Z","msg":"都係"}]}